888
00:41:35,526 --> 00:41:40,070
And our US Securities agency
and others around the globe

889
00:41:40,070 --> 00:41:42,260
really weren't
looking and watching

890
00:41:42,260 --> 00:41:49,340
until the DAO happened in 2016
