1278
01:01:26,700 --> 01:01:28,605
Act in Congress.

1279
01:01:28,605 --> 01:01:31,350
Don't you love how we
name our laws in the US?

1280
01:01:31,350 --> 01:01:32,460
The JOBS Act.

1281
01:01:35,790 --> 01:01:37,420
Accredited investors only.

1282
01:01:37,420 --> 01:01:39,930
And an accredited investor--
