1317
01:03:26,500 --> 01:03:30,300
Regulation A is
offering statement.

1318
01:03:30,300 --> 01:03:31,890
So you have to give a statement.

1319
01:03:31,890 --> 01:03:35,530
You have to give something
with the financials.

1320
01:03:35,530 --> 01:03:39,490
Not many ICOs want to
do a Reg A offering.

1321
01:03:39,490 --> 01:03:41,950
But if you were doing a startup,
if you're thinking about,

1322
01:03:41,950 --> 01:03:44,980
like, you're in one of
