1327
01:03:58,160 --> 01:04:01,030
You don't have to only limit
to accredited investors.

1328
01:04:01,030 --> 01:04:05,090
So Regulation D, only
accredited investors, generally,

1329
01:04:05,090 --> 01:04:07,980
